          "text": [
            "Downloading Reactome GMT...\n",
            "Saved to /content/reactome.gmt\n",
            "Gene sets loaded: 1,649\n",
            "Pathways used: 300  (after filtering for overlap with dataset genes)\n",
            "Genes covered by pathways: 8,822 (of 50,281 total)\n",
